TITLE: Configuring UnoCSS Blocklist
DESCRIPTION: This configuration shows how to set up a blocklist in UnoCSS to exclude specific utility classes from being generated. It demonstrates both exact string matches and regular expression patterns to block multiple classes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unocss/unocss/blob/main/docs/guide/extracting.md#2025-04-23_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: ts
