TITLE: Configuring UnoCSS Filesystem Extraction
DESCRIPTION: This configuration snippet shows how to set up UnoCSS to extract utility classes directly from the filesystem. This is useful for integrations that don't have access to the build pipeline or when working with backend frameworks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unocss/unocss/blob/main/docs/guide/extracting.md#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
