TITLE: Overriding Default UnoCSS Extractors in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to disable or override the default extractor in UnoCSS. This configuration allows for complete customization of the extraction process.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unocss/unocss/blob/main/docs/config/extractors.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { defineConfig } from 'unocss'

export default defineConfig({
  extractors: [
    // your extractors
  ],
  // disable the default extractor
  extractorDefault: false,
  // override the default extractor with your own
  extractorDefault: myExtractor,
})
```

