TITLE: SvelteKit server hook for global styles
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript code for SvelteKit's server hooks to handle the global styles placeholder replacement.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unocss/unocss/blob/main/docs/integrations/svelte-scoped.md#2025-04-23_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
/** @type {import('@sveltejs/kit').Handle} */
export async function handle({ event, resolve }) {
  const response = await resolve(event, {
    transformPageChunk: ({ html }) =>
      html.replace(
        '%unocss-svelte-scoped.global%',
        'unocss_svelte_scoped_global_styles'
      ),
  })
  return response
}
```

