TITLE: Configuring UnoCSS Pipeline Extraction in uno.config.ts
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to configure the content pipeline in UnoCSS to include additional file types for utility extraction and exclude others. It demonstrates how to customize which files UnoCSS will process during the build.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unocss/unocss/blob/main/docs/guide/extracting.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
export default defineConfig({
  content: {
    pipeline: {
      include: [
        // the default
        /\.(vue|svelte|[jt]sx|mdx?|astro|elm|php|phtml|html)($|\?)/,
        // include js/ts files
        'src/**/*.{js,ts}',
      ],
      // exclude files
      // exclude: []
    },
  },
})
```

