TITLE: Comparing Build Times of CSS Utility Frameworks
DESCRIPTION: Benchmark results showing the performance difference between UnoCSS, Windi CSS, and Tailwind CSS. The data shows build times for 1656 utilities across 50 runs, with UnoCSS being significantly faster than the alternatives.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unocss/unocss/blob/main/bench/results/2021-11-04-20-26-57.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: plaintext
CODE:
```
11/5/2021, 4:26:57 AM
1656 utilities | x50 runs (min build time)

none                              8.30 ms / delta.      0.00 ms
unocss       v0.4.15             13.58 ms / delta.      5.28 ms (x1.00)
windicss     v3.2.1             989.57 ms / delta.    981.27 ms (x185.94)
tailwindcss  v3.0.0-alpha.1    1290.96 ms / delta.   1282.66 ms (x243.05)
```

