TITLE: Installing UnoCSS with Package Managers
DESCRIPTION: Commands to install UnoCSS using different package managers like pnpm, yarn, npm, and bun.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unocss/unocss/blob/main/docs/integrations/vite.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
pnpm add -D unocss
```

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
yarn add -D unocss
```

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
npm install -D unocss
```

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
bun add -D unocss
```

