TITLE: Transformed JSX Component
DESCRIPTION: The same component after being processed by the transformer, showing how valueless attributes are converted to empty string values.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unocss/unocss/blob/main/packages-presets/transformer-attributify-jsx/README.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
export function Component() {
  return (
    <div text-red="" text-center="" text-5xl="" animate-bounce="">
      unocss
    </div>
  )
}
```

