TITLE: Configuring MDC Extractor in UnoCSS
DESCRIPTION: TypeScript configuration for setting up the MDC extractor in UnoCSS config file. This enables the extractor to process markdown files.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unocss/unocss/blob/main/docs/extractors/mdc.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import extractorMdc from '@unocss/extractor-mdc'
import { defineConfig } from 'unocss'

export default defineConfig({
  extractors: [
    extractorMdc(),
  ],
})
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Default JSX Boolean Attributes
DESCRIPTION: How JSX handles valueless attributes without the transformer by converting them to boolean attributes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unocss/unocss/blob/main/packages-presets/transformer-attributify-jsx/README.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
export function Component() {
  return (
    <div text-red={true} text-center={true} text-5xl={true} animate-bounce={true}>
      unocss
    </div>
  )
}
```

